{% set page = "index" %}
{% extends "layout.njk" %}

{% block main %}
    <div id="header-video">

    </div>
    <section id="about">
        Hi I'm Katie…

I'm a cake maker based in Thatcham, West Berkshire. I started baking and decorating cakes as a hobby from a young age with the dream that I could turn my passion into a career. Now I have a full time job as a cake decorator for a local celebration cake company, and I have started this business on the side with the aim to go full time in the near future.

